### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health


### Create Player (unique playerId!)
POST http://localhost:8080/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-001",
  "name": "Niklas",
  "region": "EUW"
}


### Create Match for player-001
POST http://localhost:8080/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-001",
  "champion": "Ahri",
  "win": true,
  "kills": 10,
  "deaths": 2,
  "assists": 6,
  "playedAt": "2026-03-01T21:30:00Z"
}


### Create another Match for player-001
POST http://localhost:8080/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-001",
  "champion": "Vayne",
  "win": true,
  "kills": 12,
  "deaths": 1,
  "assists": 3,
  "playedAt": "2026-03-01T22:15:00Z"
}


### Get all matches
GET http://localhost:8080/matches


### Get stats for player-001
GET http://localhost:8080/players/player-001/stats


### Error case: stats for non-existing player
GET http://localhost:8080/players/does-not-exist/stats


### Error case: create match with non-existing player
POST http://localhost:8080/matches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "does-not-exist",
  "champion": "Darius",
  "win": false,
  "kills": 2,
  "deaths": 10,
  "assists": 1,
  "playedAt": "2026-03-01T23:00:00Z"
}


### Error case: validation (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:8080/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riotPuuid": "",
  "name": "",
  "region": ""
}